Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:16.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年一度的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.86,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh 達令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:22.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh 達令　I Love You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都歡呼雀躍的狂歡節
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:30.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用箭射中他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:42.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜蜜甜蜜的戀愛的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:46.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:50.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要動用最後的手段
